Text: Despite Open Market Operations (OMO) maturities worth N347.7 billion, which boosted system liquidity to N694.1 billion on Thursday, the rates inched higher to 11.4 per cent and 12.3 per cent in that order.
Cause: Despite Open Market Operations (OMO) maturities worth N347.7 billion
Effect: boosted system liquidity to N694.1 billion on Thursday, the rates inched higher to 11.4 per cent and 12.3 per cent in that order.
